				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">BIHAR</h1>
				<p>One of the earliest lands of incredible Indian history, Bihar has been one of the important centers of Indian history and culture. A land of intellectuals, peace and spirituality it has hold its diverse culture and history for thousands of years. Over the years it may have lost its greatness to find things in proper but it certainly has not lost the glory once it had. Over the years great rulers have shaped it culture and society in a certain way and it has carried itself with them all along. </p><p>
        A major force in the Indian recognition and identity it is also famous for its marvelous sculptures, temples, mosques, shrines and forts. For thousands of years it has been the center for intellectuals and religious scholars. A major center for Buddhism it has held its head high for thousands of years for sending the message of peace and love. 
        </p>

